 712:src/voice.h   **** // ŌöĆŌöĆ Voice 10: snare (noise-driven) ŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌ
 713:src/voice.h   **** //   The bright, noisy cousin of the Tom ŌĆö PLAY IT BY TAPPING. Broadband noise
 714:src/voice.h   **** //   (the "wires" rattle) dominates over two tonal modes (body + a 1.8├Ś ring); a
 715:src/voice.h   **** //   wide-open filter keeps it crisp and cracking. Instant attack, short tail,
