 344:src/main.cpp  ****     // Non-blocking LED blinker: blink_start(n) queues n flashes, blink_tick()
 345:src/main.cpp  ****     // advances them between loops so glass taps still register (the old blocking
 346:src/main.cpp  ****     // flash stalled the loop up to ~2 s). Voice-select blinks the position on
